{"type": "article", "id": 9276, "title": "Star Wars 与 UGG 联名鞋子", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-07T07:17:30Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235021wFndqiRTENXoAYrs.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tStar Wars 最近频频与各种品牌联名，UGG 也来凑了个热闹。他们联手推出了一个以达斯·维达为灵感的新系列，包括各式皮鞋，豆豆鞋，休闲鞋和雪地靴，这个系列基本采用纯黑光面绗缝皮革，边上有精致的刺绣进行点缀。虽然现在正当夏日，但已经可以在全球的门店和<a href=\"http://www.uggaustralia.cn/article-campaign-172.html\" target=\"_blank\"> UGG 官方主页</a>购买，价格在 1600 到 2100 元人民币之间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235018mLbnH2jIsfrzZFgK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052350185Ya6HiNV9pAgXh3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235019OI8Kn9P4xA5LUBbc.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235019CW2VUeHBRbD3Skqr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235020PFcqy4BV5K0w8HRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235020ExXukaR3Qe5F2t8G.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}